00038 #include <stdio.h>
00039 #include <stdlib.h>
00040 #include <math.h>
00041 
00042 int shape_tria6(double *L, double *N)
00043 {
00044     double L1, L2, L3;
00045 
00046     /* Auxiliar quantities */
00047     L1 = L[0];
00048     L2 = L[1];
00049     L3 = 1.0 - L1 - L2;
00050 
00051     /* Shape function definition for node order 1-2-3-4-5-6 */
00052     N[0] = L1*(2.0*L1 - 1.0);
00053     N[1] = 4.0*L1*L2;
00054     N[2] = L2*(2.0*L2 - 1.0);
00055     N[3] = 4.0*L2*L3;
00056     N[4] = L3*(2.0*L3 - 1.0);
00057     N[5] = 4.0*L1*L3;
00058 
00059     return 0;
00060 }
